		<div type="section">
			<head>THE POST OFFICE BAN</head>
			<p><title type="journal">THE WOMAN REBEL</title> FEELS PROUD THE <org
					reg="United States Postal Service">POST OFFICE</org> AUTHORITIES DID NOT APPROVE
				OF HER. </p>
			<p>SHE SHALL BLUSH WITH SHAME IF EVER SHE BE APPROVED OF BY OFFICIALISM OR
				"COMSTOCKISM."</p>
		</div>
		<div type="section">
			<head>A WOMAN'S DUTY</head>
			<p>TO BREED LARGE FAMILIES--IN ACCORDANCE WITH <name type="law"
					reg="United States Criminal Code, Section 211">SECTION 211 OF THE CRIMINAL
					CODE</name> AS AMENDED BY THE ACT OF MARCH 4, 1911</p>
		</div>
